%99%BD%E8%AC%97-%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E5%A4%A9%E7%90%86%2F1950793438298819%2F&d=kJsi%2B77Adq7yP7dZlTZe0Izu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=87ae68e9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/notes/黃毓民/為人辯寃白謗-第一天理/1950793438298819/</a><br />\n<br />\n「偽港獨派」梁頌恆游蕙楨二人當選後，躊躇滿志，乃至在宣誓就職「躁進」賈禍，被港共政權藉詞二人宣誓無效，入稟法院司法覆核，結果遭禠奪議員資格。本土派冒起短短未及三年，即被消滅於萌芽狀態。"},{"pid":"1045daf7ecff57c5feab5cf283b97ad2c1a91736","tid":200691,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T08:45:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/14/164447_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F14%2F164447_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=30380f20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n毓民認同佢地係本土派，只係唔認同佢地係港獨派"},{"pid":"135d41b847b59b576fb3e1af4a5195041ad81731","tid":200691,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T08:49:42.000Z","msg":"同埋現實上，毓民結束自己政治生涯<br />\n只會令陳雲愈坐愈大"},{"pid":"567b8b62da51bccd320362d108e2c900b8b48a23","tid":200691,"uid":53238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T09:34:20.000Z","msg":"教主鳩達唔玩<br />\n熱狗要退出社運<br />\n陳雲而家得一條友喺 facebook 鳩 up<br />\n退唔退有咩分別"}]}